Lehi.Dr. Elmo and Rhea Eddington House:
The Dr. Elmo and Rhea Eddington House is a historic house located at 617 North 100 East in Lehi, Utah.


== Description and history ==
It is a 1-1/2 story period style cottage, built of red brick laid in a common-bond pattern, and rests on a concrete foundation, and it was built around 1932.
